   <figure>
    <p>Illustration ] To Stern Critics Here 's to stern Critics ! May they some day learn The forward lookout 's Better than the stern ! [ Illustration ] Here 's to her shadow ! May it mark the hours Upon the sundial of her life — in flowers !</p>
